By leveling up

Level Ability Cost Description

10 Sap Sipper 3 Boosts the Attack stat if hit by a Grass-type move instead of taking damage.
25 Friend Guard 5 Reduces damage done to allies.
40 Gluttony 5 Makes the Pokémon already eat a held Berry when its HP drops to half or less.
55 Triage 5 Gives priority to a healing move.
70 Cud Chew 5 An eaten Berry will be regurgitated at the end of the next turn and eaten again.
85 Scrappy 2 The Pokémon can hit Ghost-type Pokémon with Normal-and Fighting-type moves.
100 Regenerator 5 Restores a little HP when withdrawn from battle.
